---
/**
 * Custom Banner override â€” always-visible "Star on GitHub" CTA.
 * Replaces the default Starlight Banner component.
 * The .banner-pad wrapper mirrors Starlight's .content-panel padding
 * so that the inner .gh-star-banner aligns with .sl-container content.
 * PostHog tracking fires on click (posthog is loaded globally via head config).
 */
---

<div class="banner-pad">
  <div class="gh-star-banner" role="status">
    If this project helps you with EU AI Act compliance,
    <a
      href="https://github.com/venturalitica/venturalitica-sdk"
      onclick="window.posthog&&posthog.capture('github_star_clicked',{source:'banner'})"
    >
      give us a &#11088; on GitHub
    </a>
    &mdash; it helps others find us!
  </div>
</div>
